<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何重大新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 21:12:32 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>菲律宾大使没有在中国争端中寻求美国的补给支持</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-has-not-sought-us-resupply-support-china-dispute-ambassador-2024-06-26/</link><description>菲律宾驻华盛顿大使周三表示，在与中国在有争议的南中国海的对峙中，菲律宾尚未请求美国支持为其军队提供补给，并补充说美国只是提供援助菲律宾的“视觉”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 20:47:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-has-not-sought-us-resupply-support-china-dispute-ambassador-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，波音公司恢复向中国交付宽体飞机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/boeing-resuming-widebody-airplane-deliveries-china-source-says-2024-06-26/</link><description>据知情人士透露，波音公司正在恢复向中国供应宽体喷气式飞机，该项目最近几周因中国监管审查而暂停。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 20:24:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/boeing-resuming-widebody-airplane-deliveries-china-source-says-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>据彭博社报道，由于对中国进口产品征收更高关税，沃尔沃将推迟 EX30 在美国的发货</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volvo-delay-ex30s-us-shipments-due-higher-tariffs-chinese-imports-bloomberg-news-2024-06-26/</link><description>据彭博社周三报道，沃尔沃将推迟在美国交付 EX30 电动汽车，因为关税上调后，该公司将这款紧凑型 SUV 的生产转移出中国。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 19:14:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volvo-delay-ex30s-us-shipments-due-higher-tariffs-chinese-imports-bloomberg-news-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>据《Information》报道，亚马逊将推出从中国直接发货的折扣专区</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/amazon-launch-discount-section-with-direct-shipping-china-information-reports-2024-06-26/</link><description>据《The Information》周三报道，亚马逊计划在其购物网站上推出一个专区，专门销售廉价商品，这些商品可以从中国的仓库直接运送给海外消费者，并援引向中国卖家展示的幻灯片。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 17:55:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/amazon-launch-discount-section-with-direct-shipping-china-information-reports-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>秘鲁试图通过工业园激励措施吸引比亚迪汽车工厂</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/peru-trying-lure-byd-auto-plant-with-industrial-park-incentive-2024-06-26/</link><description>秘鲁总统周三会见了中国电动汽车制造商比亚迪，邀请高管在这个安第斯国家的太平洋海岸开设商店，另一家中国公司正在那里建造一个大型港口，以促进两国之间的贸易。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 16:48:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/peru-trying-lure-byd-auto-plant-with-industrial-park-incentive-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>印度给予玉米、植物油进口关税优惠</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/india-allows-imports-corn-vegetable-oils-concessional-duty-2024-06-26/</link><description>印度周三在关税配额（TRQ）下允许有限进口玉米、葵花籽油、精炼菜籽油和奶粉，进口商支付零关税或较低关税，以降低食品通胀。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 15:27:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/india-allows-imports-corn-vegetable-oils-concessional-duty-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>德中签署数据共享声明</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/germany-china-sign-declaration-data-sharing-2024-06-26/</link><description>德国一位部长周三表示，德国和中国已经签署了一份关于如何讨论跨境数据传输的意向声明，这是汽车制造商能够向德国传输数据的又一步。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 14:28:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/germany-china-sign-declaration-data-sharing-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>英国人权组织发起运动阻止 Shein 潜在的伦敦首次公开募股</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/uk-human-rights-group-launches-campaign-stop-sheins-potential-london-ipo-2024-06-26/</link><description>代表该组织的一家律师事务所周三表示，总部位于英国的人权组织“制止维吾尔族种族灭绝”已发起一项法律运动，以阻止 Shein 可能在伦敦上市，原因是对其劳工行为的担忧。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 13:39:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/uk-human-rights-group-launches-campaign-stop-sheins-potential-london-ipo-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>官方媒体称，中国在南海拦截了美国飞机投放的潜艇探测器</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-intercepts-submarine-probe-dropped-us-aircraft-south-china-sea-state-media-2024-06-26/</link><description>中国国家电视台央视旗下社交媒体帐户“愚园探天”周三称，中国最近拦截了一架美国军机投放到南海的潜艇探测器。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 11:17:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-intercepts-submarine-probe-dropped-us-aircraft-south-china-sea-state-media-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>中方驳斥美国特使有关阻碍人文交流的言论</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-rejects-us-envoys-comment-that-it-hinders-people-to-people-exchanges-2024-06-26/</link><description>中国外交部称美国大使尼古拉斯·伯恩斯周三的言论“牵强”，称其偏离了两国总统达成的重要谅解。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 08:17:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-rejects-us-envoys-comment-that-it-hinders-people-to-people-exchanges-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国开发商世茂清算听证会延期至7月31日</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinese-developer-shimaos-liquidation-hearing-adjourned-july-31-2024-06-26/</link><description>中国房地产开发商世茂集团周三在一份文件中表示，该公司再次延长了债权人有关债务重组计划的最后期限，该公司的清算案已推迟至 7 月 31 日。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 04:54:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinese-developer-shimaos-liquidation-hearing-adjourned-july-31-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>台湾报道中国“战斗巡逻”，北京誓言追捕独立“顽固分子”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-reports-renewed-chinese-military-activity-nearby-2024-06-26/</link><description>台湾国防部周三表示，中国已在台湾附近进行了另一次“联合战备巡逻”，北京表示将追查并惩罚“顽固”的台独支持者，无论他们身在何处。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 04:27:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-reports-renewed-chinese-military-activity-nearby-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>秘鲁在总统与习近平会晤前缓和中国港口争端</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/peru-eases-chinese-port-dispute-ahead-presidents-meeting-with-xi-2024-06-26/</link><description>消息人士周二称，秘鲁要求法官撤回剥夺一家中国国有企业在秘鲁太平洋沿岸建设的“大型港口”的独家经营权的请求，这在本周两国领导人会晤之前缓解了紧张局势。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 01:08:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/peru-eases-chinese-port-dispute-ahead-presidents-meeting-with-xi-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>市场准备迎接日本干预，日元兑美元跌至38年低点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/steady-dollar-sends-yen-brink-160-2024-06-26/</link><description>周三，日元兑美元汇率跌至近 38 年来的最低水平，因两个经济体之间利差较大，有利于美元，这继续打击日元，令交易员警惕日本可能采取干预措施的任何迹象。提振其货币。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 01:04:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/steady-dollar-sends-yen-brink-160-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>美国司法部称中石油将因美国出口违规行为支付 1450 万美元罚款</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/petrochina-pay-145-million-fine-us-export-violations-doj-says-2024-06-25/</link><description>美国司法部周二表示，中石油旗下的中石油国际美国公司已同意因违反美国出口法而支付总计 1,450 万美元的罚款和没收。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 22:22:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/petrochina-pay-145-million-fine-us-export-violations-doj-says-2024-06-25/</guid></item></channel></rss>